<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>12854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>趴在地板上非常不舒服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你还好吗？”一个男人低声对鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17556</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是农夫詹金斯。“会没事的。”他安慰着鲍比。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28965</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所有人都闭上眼睛。”领头的强盗大叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28966</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后从一数到一百。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都照做了。鲍比听见了重重的脚步声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他听到某个地方的门打开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47022</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们走了！”一个女人大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47023</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“……五十七，五十八……”简还在数。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她依旧紧紧闭着眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟轻轻拍了拍她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没事了，简。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们慢慢小心地从地上爬起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>外面响起了警笛声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，警察和一队救护人员就聚在了银行里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有没有谁看见了什么？”有位警官大声叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大部分都摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们戴了面具。”一个男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比举起了手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89305</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是不是看到了什么，男孩儿？”警官问鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，先生。”鲍比胆怯地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99599</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>警官将他的手放在了鲍比的肩膀上，说：“告诉我你看到了什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比描述了那些男人们进入银行之前的样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118159</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他还告诉警官他注意到的其中一个男人穿的袜子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118160</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我没看到他们的脸。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>警官给了鲍比一个大大的微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这会帮助我们找到他们的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比骄傲地挺起了胸膛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们是不是玛莎的侄子侄女？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个穿着黄色毛衣的女人走近了他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143213</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143214</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们表现得非常勇敢。”她称赞道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150406</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们害羞地笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150407</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我同意。”贝尔克先生也走到了他们这边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个小时后，警方允许所有人回家了，但很多人都不想回家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170064</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“以前从没发生过这样的事情。”基弗先生生气地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们必须抓住这些强盗。”贝尔克先生激动地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我们能做什么呢？”玛莎阿姨问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们应该一起合作保护我们的镇子。”基弗先生说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186175</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们同意地点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨邀请大家去她家里喝茶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们喝点茶之后可以更好地思考。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们帮助玛莎阿姨准备了茶水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们还拿出了一些饼干。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209943</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们实在太乖了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209944</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们真有礼貌！”人们不停地称赞孩子们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217908</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里的每个人都很好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当孩子们待在厨房里时，潘瑟对大家说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有个女人说我看上去像她孙女。”简咧开了嘴笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236393</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贝克尔先生邀请我们去他家吃晚饭。”赛伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比也开始喜欢这些邻居了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孩子们！”玛莎阿姨走进了厨房。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们能帮我再去买些面包吗？”她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊和鲍比自愿去跑腿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨把钱给了他们之后说：“快点回来，路上小心！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男孩子们向面包店跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268916</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我听说那会儿你们在银行里。”面包师对他们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>面包师问了很多问题。一些顾客也问了些问题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。”最后面包师说，“你们非常勇敢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279107</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我希望他们可以抓住这些强盗。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊要付面包钱。“这些多少钱？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>面包师摇摇头说：“不用了，这些我请客。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296276</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是送给你们这些勇敢的孩子的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296277</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男孩们向面包师道谢后就跑出去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！”鲍比直接撞到了一个路过的男人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305681</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比跌在了地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313805</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看着点儿路，小孩儿！”那个男人对着鲍比大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313806</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318648</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你还好吗？”赛伊把鲍比拉了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“赛伊！”鲍比紧紧抓住了他哥哥的手臂，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看那个男人的鞋子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330442</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个男人就要过马路了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330443</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的一只鞋子上有个洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>333713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他穿着一双红蓝杠的袜子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>